Method Detail

build

public Beacon build()
Builds a new Beacon object. There are some mandatory fields to create a beacon which are: first rssi, UUID, major and minor.

Returns:
A beacon bean with the fields set as dictated by FLUENT method calls in this builder.

buildPattern

public BeaconGroup buildPattern()
Builds a new BeaconGroup, which in essence is a Beacon object but with NO mandatory fields set unlike a Beacon object that has mandatory fields set.

Returns:
A restrictionless Beacon object.
